quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  83,1,"Halkaare woodanii …ďeen ustoo…ďe se'esir…óe."
  83,2,"∆Āeen pe'esnatoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďe …óa…ď…ďa timminaneede."
  83,3,"Si…ďe …ďetanii …ďe wolla …ďe pe'esanii …ďe usta."
  83,4,"E …ďee kan fellitaa won'de ko …ďe immintintee…ďe?"
  83,5,"Woodanii mbo √Īalawma maw…óa."
  83,6,"√Ďande yim…ďe ummanii joom binnde."
  83,7,"Ala, pellet deftere faajiree…ďe nani e sijijiin to."
  83,8,"Ko hol…óum anndinat maa ko woni SijjIiin?"
  83,9,"Ko deftere tonngaande."
  83,10,"Haray nden √Īande, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  83,11,"∆Āeen yeddoo…ďe √Īalaande njo…ďdi."
  83,12,"Yeddata mbo si wona kala palgu…óo keerol bakkadin…óo."
  83,13,"Si aayeeje amen …óeen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: ""Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe""."
  83,14,"Ala, kono muuri …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe ko…ďe njennatnoo ko."
  83,15,"Ala …ďeen de ko…ďe ha…óaa…ďe yi'ide joomi mu' en."
  83,16,"Refti pellet ko…ďe naatoo…ďe jayngol."
  83,17,"Refti …ďe wi'e:""mee…óee lepte mon …óeen; ko …óum woni ko njeddat…óon kon""."
  83,18,"Ala, pellet deftere …óiggu…ďe nani e ka illiyyiina."
  83,19,"Ko hol…óum anndinat maa ko woni Illiyyiina?"
  83,20,"Ko …óum deftere tonngaande."
  83,21,"No seedoo nde …ďur…ďe …ďadaade."
  83,22,"Pellet …ďeen …óiggu…ďe he…ďe e ne'ema."
  83,23,"E leece he…ďe ndaara."
  83,24,"Ina anndee e je'ece mu'en weltaare ne'emaaji."
  83,25,"He…ďe njarnee dola omndaako."
  83,26,"Haa…ótirde mum ko lati misku e …óuum de yo foo…óondir foo…óondiroo…ďe …ďeen."
  83,27,"Hombo e Tasniim …óuum ko seewnde …ďurnde toowde to aljanna he."
  83,28,"Sewnde nde …ďur…ďe …ďadaade njarata nde."
  83,29,"∆Āeen faajirin…ďe ngonoŇč…óna na njala …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  83,30,"Si ko …ďe mbirtiima …ďe …ďe ngona e …ďii√Īandirde."
  83,31,"Si…ďe ndu…ótiima to koreeji ma…ď…ďe …ďe ndutto ko…ďe weltii…ďe."
  83,32,"Si…ďe nji'ii…ďe …ďe mbi'a …ďe ko …ďe majju…ďe."
  83,33,"∆Āe nelaaka e dow muenn ngam reende …ďe."
  83,34,"Hannde de gooŇč…óin…ďe njala he'efer…ďe."
  83,35,"E le'ece he…ďe ndaara."
  83,36,"Mbele he'efer…ďe njo…ďaama ko…ďe mba…óatnoo ko."
